@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api

### Listar Usuários
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

### Criar Usuário
# @name createUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Exemplo",
  "email": "joao@exemplo.com"
}

### Buscar Usuário por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{createUser.response.body.id}}

---

### Listar Tipos de Eventos
GET {{baseUrl}}/event-types

### Criar Tipo de Evento
# @name createType
POST {{baseUrl}}/event-types
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Concerto Musical"
}

---

### Listar Eventos
GET {{baseUrl}}/events

### Criar Evento
# @name createEvent
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Orquestra Filarmônica",
  "eventTypeId": "{{createType.response.body.id}}",
  "date": "2024-11-15T19:30:00",
  "startSales": "2024-09-01T10:00:00",
  "endSales": "2024-11-14T23:59:59",
  "price": 120.0
}

