### Listar Vendas
GET {{baseUrl}}/sales

### Criar Venda
# @name createSale
POST {{baseUrl}}/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{createUser.response.body.id}}",
  "eventId": "{{createEvent.response.body.id}}",
  "saleStatus": "EM_ABERTO"
}

### Confirmar Pagamento
PUT {{baseUrl}}/sales/{{createSale.response.body.id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "saleStatus": "PAGO"
}
